<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Refund Policy - CozySpot</title>
		<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

	</head>
	<body class="bg-black text-white font-['Inter'] antialiased">
		<!-- Navigation -->
		<div id="navigation-container"></div>

		<div id="ambient-bg">
			<div class="shooting-star"></div>
			<div class="shooting-star"></div>
			<div class="shooting-star"></div>
		</div>

		<div id="scroll-progress"></div>

		<!-- Main Content -->
		<main class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
				<!-- Header -->
				<div class="mb-12">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
					<p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Last updated: January 17, 2026</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Quick Summary -->
				<div class="mb-12 p-6 bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-xl">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">Quick Summary</h2>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-white/80">
						<li>✓ <strong>14-day</strong> return window from delivery date</li>
						<li>✓ Items must be <strong>unused and in original packaging</strong></li>
						<li>✓ Contact us at <a href="mailto:cozyspot.team@gmail.com" class="text-purple-400">cozyspot.team@gmail .com</a> to start a return</li>
						<li>✓ Refunds processed within <strong>5-10 business days</strong></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Content -->
				<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-white/70">
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Return Eligibility</h2>
						<p>
							We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy with your order, you may request a return within <strong>14 days</strong> of receiving your
							item.
						</p>

						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">To be eligible for a return:</h3>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Item must be unused, unwashed, and in its original condition</li>
							<li>Item must be in original packaging with all tags attached</li>
							<li>You must provide proof of purchase (order number or receipt)</li>
							<li>Return request must be made within 14 days of delivery</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
						<p>The following items cannot be returned:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Items that have been used, washed, or altered</li>
							<li>Items without original packaging or tags</li>
							<li>Items marked as "Final Sale" or "Non-Returnable"</li>
							<li>Personalized or custom-made items</li>
							<li>Items returned after the 14-day window</li>
							<li>Gift cards</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. How to Request a Return</h2>
						<p>To initiate a return, please follow these steps:</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-3">
							<li>
								<strong>Contact Us:</strong> Email us at <a href="mailto:cozyspot.team@gmail.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">cozyspot.team@gmail.com</a> with:
								<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
									<li>Your order number</li>
									<li>Item(s) you wish to return</li>
									<li>Reason for return</li>
									<li>Photos of the item (if applicable)</li>
								</ul>
							</li>
							<li><strong>Await Approval:</strong> We will review your request and respond within 24 hours with return instructions.</li>
							<li><strong>Ship the Item:</strong> Once approved, ship the item back to the provided address.</li>
							<li><strong>Receive Refund:</strong> After we receive and inspect the item, we'll process your refund.</li>
						</ol>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Return Shipping Costs</h2>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div class="p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">If we made an error:</h4>
								<p>We will cover return shipping costs if you received a wrong, defective, or damaged item.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Change of mind:</h4>
								<p>Customer is responsible for return shipping costs. We recommend using a trackable shipping method.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. Refund Process</h2>
						<p>Once we receive and inspect your return, we will notify you via email about the approval or rejection of your refund.</p>

						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">If approved:</h3>
						<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Refund will be processed to your original payment method</li>
							<li>Processing time: 5-10 business days</li>
							<li>Bank processing may take additional 3-5 business days</li>
							<li>Original shipping costs are non-refundable (unless we made an error)</li>
						</ul>

						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-2">Partial Refunds:</h3>
						<p>We may issue a partial refund for items that show signs of use, are missing parts, or are not in original condition.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
						<p>If you receive a damaged or defective item:</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery</li>
							<li>Include photos of the damage/defect and packaging</li>
							<li>We will arrange a replacement or full refund at no additional cost</li>
						</ol>
						<p class="mt-4 text-yellow-400/80"><strong>Important:</strong> Please inspect your package upon delivery and document any damage before opening.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Exchanges</h2>
						<p>We currently do not offer direct exchanges. If you need a different size, color, or product:</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Return the original item for a refund</li>
							<li>Place a new order for the desired item</li>
						</ol>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Late or Missing Refunds</h2>
						<p>If you haven't received your refund after the stated processing time:</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
							<li>Check your bank account/credit card statement again</li>
							<li>Contact your credit card company (refunds can take time to post)</li>
							<li>Contact your bank (there may be processing time)</li>
							<li>
								If you've done all of this and still haven't received your refund, contact us at
								<a href="mailto:cozyspot.team@gmail.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">cozyspot.team@gmail.com</a>
							</li>
						</ol>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">9. Cancellations</h2>
						<p>You may cancel your order within <strong>12 hours</strong> of placing it, provided it has not been shipped. To cancel, contact us immediately with your order number.</p>
						<p class="mt-2">Once an order has been shipped, it cannot be cancelled. You will need to wait to receive it and then initiate a return.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
						<p>For any questions about returns or refunds:</p>
						<div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
							<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:cozyspot.team@gmail.com" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">cozyspot.team@gmail.com</a></p>
							<p class="mt-2"><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</p>
							<p class="mt-2"><strong>Subject Line:</strong> Include "Return Request - [Order Number]"</p>
						</div>
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

		<!-- Footer -->
		<div id="footer-container"></div>

		<script src="script.js"></script>
		<script>
			fetch('navigation.html')
				.then(res => res.text())
				.then(html => {
					document.getElementById('navigation-container').innerHTML = html
					if (typeof runMenuScripts === 'function') runMenuScripts()
				})

			fetch('footer.html')
				.then(res => res.text())
				.then(html => {
					document.getElementById('footer-container').innerHTML = html
				})
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
